snippet.title: Assassin’s Creed Syndicate: Evie Frye Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Get a first look at one of the stars of Assassin’s Creed Syndicate, Evie Frye, and the variety of deadly weapons she employs in her fight alongside Jacob and the rest of The Rooks to control London’s criminal underground. From her unique version of the signature Assassin’s hidden blade to her elegant cane sword and deadly throwing knives, Evie is a force to be reckoned with.

May contain content inappropriate for children.  Visit www.esrb.org for rating information.
